ğŸ‘‰ npm = handles JS/CSS packages (frontend).
ğŸ‘‰ Webpack/Vite/Rollup = bundles/minifies assets for production.


-------------- shortcut ---------------
npm init -y              = (ğŸ‘‰ Creates package.json)
copy pest package name from npmjs.com (e.g =     npm i choices.js    )  ğŸ‘‰ Downloads Choices.js into node_modules/

npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-cli        ğŸ‘‰ Installs webpack

npm run build         ( builds the necessery file and move it to "assets/js" ) now no need "node/modules"
enqueue that new js file into your plugin 
Now use the package

